title: SanDisk SDSDU-064G-A11 64GB Ultra SDXC UHS-I Card 30MB/s (Class 10)
description: Combining fast performance and generous capacity, the SanDisk Ultra SDHC is an ideal storage choice for compact to mid-range point-and-shoot cameras and camcorders. This versatile card offers twice the Speed of an ordinary memory card, so you can take more pictures with less lag time. These cards come in a variety of capacities and feature a shock-resistant, water and temperature-proof design. SDHC (8-32GB) Cards are compatible with all SDHC/SDXC and SDHC-I/SDXC-I (UHS-I) enabled host devices. SDXC (64GB) card is compatible with SDXC and SDXC-I (UHS-I) enabled host devices. Don't miss the moment. Be ready with double the Speed and the highest video performance.;
